---
layout: page.vto
type: meta-work
title: DRAGONzine
---

<p>DRAGONzine was my attempt to regularly edit and publish a web-based
magazine of sci-fi/fantasy in High School, even taking contributions
from a few other students. At its peak I wrote around 5k-6k words in a
month. Here are most of my own preserved contributions:</p>

<dl>
{{ for id, date of dzissues }}
   <dt id="issue{{ id }}">#{{ id }}</dt>
   <dd class="text-info">Published: {{ date.toLocaleString(undefined, { year: 'numeric', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' }) }}</dd>
   {{ for story of search.pages(`dz_issue=${id}`) }}
   <dd class="title"><a href="{{ story.url }}">{{ story.title }}</a></dd>
   {{ if story.excerpt }}
   <dd>{{ story.excerpt }}</dd>
   {{ /if }}
   {{ /for }}
{{ /for }}
</dl>
